name: NYDailyNews
text:
Yankees pitcher James Paxton wanted a protective “L screen” in front of the mound before his simulated innings, after Masahiro Tanaka took a line drive to the head. 

Tanaka is under MLB concussion protocol. "We’ll take it day by day," Aaron Boone said.
